Interface Query<Q extends Query<Q>>

  • Type Parameters:
    Q - concrete subtype
    All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Subinterfaces:
    JDOQLQuery<T>, JPQLQuery<T>, SQLCommonQuery<Q>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractHibernateQuery, AbstractHibernateSQLQuery, AbstractJDOQuery, AbstractJPAQuery, AbstractJPASQLQuery, AbstractSQLQuery, AbstractSQLQuery, AbstractSQLQuery, HibernateQuery, HibernateSQLQuery, JDOQuery, JDOSQLQuery, JPAQuery, JPAQueryBase, JPASQLQuery, MySQLQuery, OracleQuery, PostgreSQLQuery, ProjectableSQLQuery, SQLQuery, SQLServerQuery, TeradataQuery

    public interface Query<Q extends Query<Q>>
extends SimpleQuery<Q>
    Query defines the main query interface of the fluent query language.

    Note that the from method has been left out, since there are implementation specific variants of it.
